{
  "stem": "25651.10",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How do they get them?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They don't get them officially, but they get them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And no matter how much they talk in Parliament about it, they can't stop it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was the same in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, and he told me all kinds of things as well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I had--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, later, I'll tell you later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, he didn't tell me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't really tell me secrets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- for example, he once told me, [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] do you know how we save fuel?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So, I say, what do you mean save fuel?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, it takes a long time to burn a body, so we put three together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We put a fat man, and a woman, and a child-- you know, the pallets that are wheeled in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It takes 15 minutes to burn, and then it's red hot, so you can't actually load the next pallet.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they had a-- he was describing that they had 12 of these crematorium ovens.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had to load them in sequence, and they save fuel by burning human fat, because the people who came.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he said, the worst thing is when we are burning bodies of people who die, because they are so thin that the bones won't burn.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "When we switch off, the bones are left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The kinds of stories-- he, he was relieving his own-- his own trauma and his own fears.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But he would trade, you know, vodka for salami, or clothes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was a sort of interchange of goods going on all the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
